{"tid":1715823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫迪歷暗示有機會加盟意甲","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:50:06.000Z","uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"661215b6204064b8deaf7626a1ba6424db220702","tid":1715823,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"莫迪歷合約將在季尾完結，自然有不少消息指他將會離開班拿貝。事實上，去年夏天便曾傳出莫迪歷轉會巴黎聖日耳門，再對上一年則是國際米蘭。然而，根據最新的訪問，似乎意甲會是莫迪歷的真正目的地。<br />\n莫迪歷在接受意大利《天空體育》訪問時表示：「我喜歡意大利，這裏與克羅地亞接距離很近。因為不少國家隊隊友在此踢球，我也會看意甲賽事。意大利人十分美妙，有很多方面都與我們克羅地亞人相似。看看有朝一日我會否在意大利踢球吧，但我不能談論這個問題，因為我是皇家馬德里的球員，我喜歡效力皇馬，現時我只看到自己的未來在這裏。」<br />\n莫迪歷效力皇馬8年以來曾贏得1次西甲及4次歐聯，他在2018年世界盃憑出色表現帶領克羅地亞殺入決賽獲得亞軍，個人勇奪金球獎打破美斯及C朗的壟斷。不過，34歲的莫迪歷被指近期表現下滑，在今季西甲暫時只有3場正選上陣。 （<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=5da9a250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n唔係會入祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4de156ec858fc44588714685bca4dadde2c769e","tid":1715823,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"擺明去祖記啦"},{"pid":"9ba17f2596032524bfa1a0dbdb15bec856da75d8","tid":1715823,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"去祖 -&gt; 助攻c朗<br />\n去國米 -&gt; 助攻lkk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81854f54a761322530e12bc38ca918dd6a85039b","tid":1715823,"uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"快d lan 嘔返個金球出來"},{"pid":"690e712d777d0b017bec227d4061a8c9f08618e5","tid":1715823,"uid":216975,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"應該羅馬啦 最有前途"},{"pid":"a719ca39d8e2e5937b873cc8d859180a00ac157d","tid":1715823,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"是但一隊米蘭啦"},{"pid":"91ce8b540cec974e4231089b632c892337a6fada","tid":1715823,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba17f2596032524bfa1a0dbdb15bec856da75d8","tid":1715823,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"去祖 -&gt; 助攻c朗<br />\n去國米 -&gt; 助攻lkk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:47:22.000Z","msg":"牙朗聯賽入5球<br />\n渣古聯賽入9球"},{"pid":"6fe095bda7b734f4254b58502c62b36c4d99016e","tid":1715823,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"老人院聯賽"},{"pid":"99e6e74ba02bd9f81844e934c05d8889b2606ccd","tid":1715823,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a719ca39d8e2e5937b873cc8d859180a00ac157d","tid":1715823,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"是但一隊米蘭啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"而家國米同A米差好遠喎 好難是但一隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}